Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TysonBio AC500/AC800/AC500 Pro/AC800 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems for quantitative glucose measurement in capillary whole blood using electrochemical biosensor technology.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertip, palm, or forearm for self-testing at home (single-patient use) or for multiple-patient use in professional healthcare settings as an aid to monitor diabetes control; not for diagnosis/screening of diabetes or neonatal use.
